---
title: Full sample taco recipe
author: Tim Chase
servings: 4
tags:
 - example
 - texmex
---

= Filling

Heat @oil{1%tsp} in a #skillet{10in} on medium.

Chop @onion{1/4}.

Add chopped onion and @red pepper flakes{1/4-1/2%tsp}.

Meanwhile microwave @veggie burgers{2} for ~{1%min},
flip them over, and microwave for another ~{30%sec}.

Chop up the veggie burgers.

Saute until onion is translucent.

Add @cumin{1%tsp},
@chili powder{1%Tbsp},
@dried oregano{1/2%Tbsp},
@taco seasoning{1/2%Tbsp},
@garlic powder{1/4%tsp},
and the chopped veggie-burger.

= corn

In a #saucepan{6%in},
bring @water{1%cup} to a boil.

Add @frozen corn{1½%cups},
return to a boil,
and remove from heat.


